Simple and Delicious

   This smoky avocado toast with miso recipe is exactly that ‚Äì simple and
   delicious. It‚Äôs one of those breakfast dishes that will make you look
   forward to getting up in the morning. Just like a great cup of coffee,
   it‚Äôs a wonderful way to start the day!

